WEBVTT

00:00:00.484 --> 00:00:04.055
Shmuel Bushkin, OCTOBER TWENTY-SIX, NINETEEN NINETY-SEVEN.

00:00:05.952 --> 00:00:07.279
iz,

00:00:07.555 --> 00:00:13.016
geyt on vayter, zayt azoy gut. ir hot, genumen redn vegn, ven di daytshn zaynen arayn.

00:00:10.710 --> 00:00:12.683
⟨m-⟩ vegn mayn,

00:00:12.683 --> 00:00:14.844
vegn mayn bruder, ershtn⟨s⟩.

00:00:14.844 --> 00:00:17.842
dos heyst, hobn mir gebrakht dem bruder. er i-...

00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:18.922
velkher bruder, un vi heyst er?

00:00:17.848 --> 00:00:20.778
dem dritn bruder, vos er iz gevezn in,

00:00:20.903 --> 00:00:24.508
in kinder-gortn. ho- er hot gelebt hintern shtot,

00:00:25.172 --> 00:00:26.207
un mir hobn...

00:00:25.172 --> 00:00:28.186
s'iz geven a kinder-gortn vos er hot...?

00:00:26.207 --> 00:00:28.862
a ki- ⟨ya,⟩ hintern shtot.

00:00:29.492 --> 00:00:30.734
dos ⟨iz,⟩

00:00:31.450 --> 00:00:35.068
nit in Rige, ober s'iz gevezn, ⟨s'-⟩...

00:00:32.226 --> 00:00:33.165
uhuh.

00:00:33.711 --> 00:00:35.291
er hot gelebt dort?

00:00:35.652 --> 00:00:37.418
vo- ikh farshtey nisht.

00:00:37.575 --> 00:00:40.556
er iz, er ⟨g-⟩ er fleg geyn dort yedn tog?

00:00:38.352 --> 00:00:40.250
in Let-...

00:00:40.250 --> 00:00:42.986
neyn, neyn. dortn hot er gelebt tog un nakht.

00:00:43.414 --> 00:00:44.600
dos iz gevezn,

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:46.835
nu, vi a kurort.

00:00:47.447 --> 00:00:49.938
tsu fir-finef yor iz er geven?

00:00:49.405 --> 00:00:52.048
er iz gevezn, neyn, er iz gevezn dray yor.

00:00:52.780 --> 00:00:54.034
⟨un er⟩ hot gelebt dort?

00:00:52.847 --> 00:00:53.983
a dray yor.

00:00:53.983 --> 00:00:56.839
ya, in a kinder-gort- a kin⟨der-gor-⟩...

00:00:54.034 --> 00:00:57.364
iz dos a sakh kinder? ikh hob nisht gehert vegn,...

00:00:57.167 --> 00:00:58.140
ya.

00:00:57.869 --> 00:01:01.915
a sakh mentshn hobn dos geton mit zeyere kinder? gelozt lebn...?

00:01:00.070 --> 00:01:01.649
vi den? ale ki-

00:01:01.649 --> 00:01:06.298
m- ale, hot um- undzere kinder zaynen ge- oykhet durkhgegangen ale durkh,

00:01:06.298 --> 00:01:07.226
kinder-gortn.

00:01:07.056 --> 00:01:10.037
ir zayt oykh geven bay aza kinder-gortn?

00:01:07.226 --> 00:01:08.197
zey flegn oyf⟨z-⟩...

00:01:09.165 --> 00:01:10.200
ya.

00:01:10.110 --> 00:01:13.293
tsu dray yor? ir, un ir hot gevoynt dort,...?

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:11.420
vi den?

00:01:12.692 --> 00:01:15.419
tsu dray, tsu fir, vi de-? neyn!

00:01:15.426 --> 00:01:18.393
ikh hob gelebt in Rige, nor do zaynen zey oyf

00:01:18.393 --> 00:01:19.706
zumer.

00:01:19.257 --> 00:01:22.980
oh, oyf a zumer-CAMP! a SUMMER CAMP, a zumer-lager,

00:01:19.746 --> 00:01:24.758
oyf zumer-⟨ts-⟩, ya, in, zum⟨er⟩ zaynen zey aroysgeforn.

00:01:23.188 --> 00:01:24.290
a kurort.

00:01:24.290 --> 00:01:25.471
antshuldikt.

00:01:24.758 --> 00:01:27.316
hot men im gedarft brengen. mir hobn im gebrakht.

00:01:25.922 --> 00:01:27.181
itster farshtey ikh.

00:01:28.318 --> 00:01:29.780
 nu, un

00:01:30.428 --> 00:01:32.514
di zakh iz derfun az

00:01:33.381 --> 00:01:37.526
me hot gedarft zey rateven, di mamen. der tate iz nit gevezn,

00:01:37.549 --> 00:01:40.800
vayle der tate hobn di rusn tsugenumen,

00:01:41.127 --> 00:01:42.842
ikh veys nit vos dortn,

00:01:43.303 --> 00:01:45.524
zey hobn... vi heyst es,

00:01:46.662 --> 00:01:48.995
az me ruft arayn, ruft ayn

00:01:48.995 --> 00:01:50.148
in armey?

00:01:49.969 --> 00:01:53.231
uhuh. a DRAFT. azoy vi me ruft a DRAFT.

00:01:50.728 --> 00:01:54.142
azoy... y- ya. hot men im ayngerufn,

00:01:54.142 --> 00:01:56.021
kh'veys nit oyf vos far a arbet.

00:01:56.466 --> 00:02:01.235
 un di mame iz gevezn in shtub un ikh un nokh di tsvey brider.

00:02:02.727 --> 00:02:04.678
ikh gib a kuk az

00:02:05.342 --> 00:02:10.274
es kumen on, lebn undz, lebn undzer hoyz, iz ongekumen a bloer

00:02:10.274 --> 00:02:11.461
AVTOBUS,

00:02:11.637 --> 00:02:14.148
un in dem bloem AVTOBUS

00:02:14.148 --> 00:02:18.819
geyen arayn men-, me- vayber mit kinder,

00:02:19.332 --> 00:02:21.182
a fuler AVTOBUS.

00:02:22.197 --> 00:02:25.693
⟨b-⟩ bin ikh shoyn aroyfgelofn. ikh hob gefregt bayn,

00:02:25.693 --> 00:02:26.525
