00:02:26.525 --> 00:02:27.850
"vos badayt es?"

00:02:27.850 --> 00:02:30.297
hobn zey gezogt az me firt zey aroys fun

00:02:30.297 --> 00:02:31.174
Rige,

00:02:31.174 --> 00:02:32.927
vayle di daytshn zaynen

00:02:33.085 --> 00:02:34.597
gornit vayt.

00:02:35.397 --> 00:02:37.766
un ale yidn, merstn teyl.

00:02:38.164 --> 00:02:41.102
bin ikh shoyn aroyfgelofn in der sh- in shtub.

00:02:41.102 --> 00:02:44.621
mayn mame shteyt baym plit un bakt latkes,

00:02:45.218 --> 00:02:50.139
un ikh heys ir shoyn es altsding tsuzamenpakn.

00:02:51.090 --> 00:02:52.791
nu, zi vil nit forn,

00:02:52.791 --> 00:02:55.488
vayle zi farshteyt nit oyf azoy fil,

00:02:55.849 --> 00:02:59.167
oyf vifl es iz geferlekh tsu blaybn in Rige.

00:03:01.418 --> 00:03:05.276
nu, ober ikh hob ir mitn bruder,

00:03:05.299 --> 00:03:09.512
hobn mir geholf- hobn mir tsuzamengepakt vos zi hot gekent,

00:03:09.619 --> 00:03:12.144
dortn di bisl gelt vos iz gevezn,

00:03:12.387 --> 00:03:13.562
hobn mir

00:03:13.568 --> 00:03:15.148
avekgegebn ir,

00:03:15.829 --> 00:03:19.428
un ikh hob ir avekgefirt nit in dem AVTOBUS,

00:03:19.428 --> 00:03:20.737
ober

00:03:21.178 --> 00:03:23.619
s'iz gevezn, umgefer, a f-

00:03:24.958 --> 00:03:28.111
a finf hundert meter vayter ⟨zay-⟩, dortn iz oykhet,

00:03:28.111 --> 00:03:30.353
