dos iz di REYS- di b- AVTOBUSn vos flegn

00:03:34.186 --> 00:03:35.516
firn mentshn

00:03:35.809 --> 00:03:39.204
iber,... ot azoy vi do geyen di AVTOBUSn.

00:03:38.256 --> 00:03:40.518
tsu der arbet un azoy vayter?

00:03:39.204 --> 00:03:40.087
ya.

00:03:40.332 --> 00:03:46.637
nor do, in d⟨e-⟩ in di tsayt, hot men zey genumen aroystsufirn, tsu rateven mentshn.

00:03:40.737 --> 00:03:42.182
un,...

00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:48.673
un di rus- di rusishe

00:03:48.673 --> 00:03:52.087
oytoritetn hobn dos, gefodert?

00:03:50.777 --> 00:03:53.547
ya, di rusn, dos hobn gemakht di rusn.

00:03:53.595 --> 00:03:55.529
nu, ikh hob bavizn

00:03:55.958 --> 00:03:58.382
zey arayntsuzetsn in

00:03:58.877 --> 00:04:00.197
AVTOBUS.

00:03:58.877 --> 00:04:01.453
 di mame mit di tsvey brider?

00:04:00.197 --> 00:04:02.398
di mamen mit tsvey brider.

00:04:03.822 --> 00:04:05.621
mayn vayb's,

00:04:05.830 --> 00:04:06.937
mit di,

00:04:07.618 --> 00:04:09.367
mit di mamen,

00:04:10.015 --> 00:04:14.987
un oykhet mit tsvey, mit, m- mit f- mit dray kin- zey zaynen dray kinder gevezn.

00:04:14.807 --> 00:04:18.473
ayer vayb, vos iz demolt geven a, a khaverte?

00:04:17.134 --> 00:04:18.134
⟨a⟩...

00:04:18.134 --> 00:04:21.843
