dos hot zi mir shpeter dertseylt az zey zaynen geforn tsuzamen

00:04:25.860 --> 00:04:27.524
in, in Rusland.

00:04:27.261 --> 00:04:28.554
mit ayer mamen?

00:04:28.071 --> 00:04:29.077
ya.

00:04:29.353 --> 00:04:33.144
iz, ayer, ayer froy, vos iz itst ayer froy, demolt

00:04:33.353 --> 00:04:34.795
iz zi geven...

00:04:33.893 --> 00:04:37.009
⟨iz⟩ geven a kind. zi iz geve⟨z⟩n a kind.

00:04:34.795 --> 00:04:37.785
a kind? vos ir, ober ir hot zikh gekent demolt?

00:04:37.386 --> 00:04:39.810
i- ikh hob ir nit gekent.

00:04:39.259 --> 00:04:41.058
o, nit gekent. UNK

00:04:39.934 --> 00:04:43.758
nu, vayle ikh bin mit zeks yor elter, finf a halb yor elter.

00:04:42.313 --> 00:04:43.302
o.

00:04:43.410 --> 00:04:46.154
o, nor shpeter hot ir zikh dervust vegn dem.

00:04:43.815 --> 00:04:46.728
ikh hob ⟨ober⟩ shpeter az, nokh di krig.

00:04:47.713 --> 00:04:48.697
 ober

00:04:48.697 --> 00:04:50.593
me hot zey geratevet.

00:04:53.755 --> 00:04:56.013
⟨v-⟩ di...

00:04:55.813 --> 00:04:59.705
⟨u⟩ntshuldikt, ⟨v-⟩ nokh a mol, far vos zayt ir nisht geforn mit zey?

00:04:58.918 --> 00:04:59.958
ikh bin,

00:05:00.437 --> 00:05:03.184
ikh bin geshtanen in AVTOBUS,

00:05:03.184 --> 00:05:06.067
un ikh bin aroysgeshprungen fun AVTOBUS,

00:05:06.411 --> 00:05:08.230
vayle ikh hob gehat

00:05:08.230 --> 00:05:10.472
fun mayn mame's tsad

00:05:10.562 --> 00:05:12.817
der zeyde, di boben,

00:05:13.110 --> 00:05:16.394
tantes. kh'hob zey gevelt geyn rateven.

00:05:16.418 --> 00:05:18.994
kh'hob gehat fun mayn tate's tsad

00:05:19.017 --> 00:05:20.878
bobes, zeydes, mit

00:05:20.878 --> 00:05:22.014
tantes.

00:05:22.273 --> 00:05:25.692
ikh bin gelofn fun eynem tsum tsveytn. ikh hob zey gevelt

00:05:25.800 --> 00:05:27.194
rateven.

00:05:27.370 --> 00:05:30.353
yene hobn zikh opgezogt, fun mayn tate's

00:05:30.353 --> 00:05:31.177
tsad.

00:05:31.335 --> 00:05:33.759
un fun mayn z- mame's

00:05:33.850 --> 00:05:35.508
hob ikh zey ayngeredt.

00:05:35.508 --> 00:05:38.011
hobn zey genumen, ayngepakt zikh,

00:05:38.170 --> 00:05:43.271
un mir zaynen gegangen; keyn AVTOBUSn zaynen shoyn nit gevezn. biz vanen zey hobn dos altsding geton

00:05:43.271 --> 00:05:44.559
iz shoyn gevorn,

00:05:44.646 --> 00:05:49.641
⟨,⟩ finf a zeyger, zaynen shoyn ale AVTOBUSn gevezn avekgef-... ⟨iz⟩ hobn mir

00:05:49.641 --> 00:05:51.312
g- zaynen mir gegangen

00:05:51.312 --> 00:05:54.093
oyfn vokzal, vu es shteyen

00:05:55.348 --> 00:05:56.670
vagones;

00:05:56.670 --> 00:05:57.671
efsher

00:05:57.745 --> 00:05:58.852
dortn...

00:05:59.027 --> 00:06:04.792
nor der zeyde iz gevezn tsvey un zibtsik yor, di bobe iz gevezn tsvey un zibtsik yor;

00:06:05.642 --> 00:06:09.602
zey kenen nit loyfn, zey kenen nit geyn.

00:06:09.743 --> 00:06:11.897
hot men zikh ongehoybn bay mir betn:

00:06:14.468 --> 00:06:17.789
"kum oyf tsurik aheym. vos es vet zayn, vet zayn.

00:06:17.789 --> 00:06:20.360
mir kenen nit; es platst di harts."

00:06:21.825 --> 00:06:24.384
hob ikh gemuzt geyn mit zey oyf tsurik aheym.

00:06:24.728 --> 00:06:27.709
un dortn hot derlangt a SNARYAD, a...

00:06:27.900 --> 00:06:29.581
ir veyst vos iz a SNARYAD?

00:06:29.672 --> 00:06:30.948
a bombe.

00:06:31.393 --> 00:06:33.074
lebn undz.

00:06:33.857 --> 00:06:37.682
nu, a meter ts- fuftsn fun undz.

00:06:38.143 --> 00:06:39.928
⟨hot⟩ gemakht a groyse

00:06:39.928 --> 00:06:40.803
lokh

00:06:41.485 --> 00:06:42.677
in der erd,

00:06:43.172 --> 00:06:46.726
un der zeyde mit di boben mit di tantes hobn zikh dershrokn.

00:06:47.526 --> 00:06:49.406
kh'hob zikh aleyn oykhet dershrokn.

00:06:50.361 --> 00:06:52.329
un ikh hob zey gebrakht aheym,

00:06:53.533 --> 00:06:55.872
un zey zaynen geblibn azoy.

00:06:57.162 --> 00:06:58.219
un

00:06:58.154 --> 00:07:02.421
un, un ir hot, ir hot nisht mer gekent forn? s'iz geven tsu shpet?

00:06:58.798 --> 00:07:00.282
dem ersht-...

00:07:00.891 --> 00:07:04.196
un ikh hob shoyn nit, neyn. ikh hob shoyn nit gehat vu tsu forn.

00:07:04.452 --> 00:07:08.136
ikh bin shoyn geblibn aleyn, ⟨dos⟩, mit zey tsuzamen.

00:07:08.653 --> 00:07:14.171
vifl, rekhnt ir, protsent, az, yidn zaynen geblibn un nisht gekent

00:07:14.171 --> 00:07:14.885
avek,

00:07:14.885 --> 00:07:16.241
fun ayer gegnt?

00:07:17.293 --> 00:07:19.902
umgefer, in Letland

00:07:20.854 --> 00:07:22.366
iz gevezn

00:07:22.963 --> 00:07:25.302
iber draysik toyznt yidn.

00:07:32.346 --> 00:07:34.348
avek zaynen efsher,

00:07:36.362 --> 00:07:39.309
efsher tsen, tsvelf protsent,

00:07:39.872 --> 00:07:41.300
nit mer.

00:07:39.872 --> 00:07:45.291
ober in ayer gegnt, oyf ayere gasn, ⟨ir⟩, yed- yeder, yeder tsvey?

00:07:42.488 --> 00:07:44.813
ah, fun undzere gasn zaynen avek

00:07:44.813 --> 00:07:47.240
dray, dray AVTOBUSn,

00:07:47.635 --> 00:07:51.605
dray oder fir AVTOBUSn. nu, nemt, in yeder AVTOBUS iz gevezn,

00:07:51.605 --> 00:07:53.214
nu, fuftsik man.

00:07:53.895 --> 00:07:58.564
iz, a sakh yidn, a s- nisht keyn sakh zaynen geblibn?

00:07:54.081 --> 00:07:56.184
iz a tsvey hundert man.

00:07:57.608 --> 00:07:58.676
nit keyn s-

00:07:58.676 --> 00:08:00.217
nit keyn sakh zaynen

00:08:00.814 --> 00:08:04.520
avekgeforn. geblibn UNK geblibn.

00:08:01.168 --> 00:08:03.440
o, a sakh zaynen geblibn.

00:08:04.172 --> 00:08:06.393
fun di yunge un di

00:08:05.440 --> 00:08:06.440
yu-

00:08:06.440 --> 00:08:09.701
fun yunge un fun di eltere, ⟨a-⟩ ya.

00:08:06.448 --> 00:08:09.194
f- mishpokhes mit kinder zaynen geblibn?

00:08:10.163 --> 00:08:11.507
iz, az

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:13.919
dem ershtn yuli

00:08:14.331 --> 00:08:16.232
zaynen arayn di daytshn,

00:08:16.255 --> 00:08:18.375
bin ikh shoyn gevezn oyfn gas.

00:08:18.533 --> 00:08:20.931
me darf dokh a kuk gebn; s'zaynen gekumen

00:08:20.931 --> 00:08:23.572
naye soldatn. ikh hob zey keyn mol nit gezen.

00:08:24.102 --> 00:08:26.559
zey zaynen gekumen grade oyfn vinkl

00:08:28.843 --> 00:08:31.149
vu ikh leb, LĀČPLĒŠA

00:08:31.341 --> 00:08:32.718
un GOGOĻA.

00:08:32.808 --> 00:08:37.257
hobn z⟨ey⟩ avekgeshtelt glaykh, ale mit farkasherte arbl,

00:08:37.618 --> 00:08:41.830
di, vi heldn. nu, zey zaynen, ⟨⟩, vi heldn zaynen zey gekumen.

00:08:42.241 --> 00:08:44.868
un hobn avekgeshtelt a kleyne pushke.

00:08:45.145 --> 00:08:48.649
 nu a pu- ⟨a s-⟩ vi heyst?, ir veyst vos a pushke iz?

00:08:49.093 --> 00:08:50.977
azoy rufn mir es oyf yidish.

00:08:52.131 --> 00:08:53.576
un,

00:08:54.780 --> 00:08:57.271
un hobn zikh genumen klaybn daytshn.

00:08:59.438 --> 00:09:01.474
un vu es flegt geyn a daytsh,

00:09:02.121 --> 00:09:03.971
flegn mentshn nokhloyfn.

00:09:04.332 --> 00:09:07.009
VOT, vi, vi es volt ⟨ge⟩kumen fun,

00:09:07.842 --> 00:09:10.943
fun, fun mars, voltn gekumen,

00:09:10.943 --> 00:09:12.791
mentshn. azoy zaynen

00:09:12.791 --> 00:09:14.805
ale nokhgelofn di daytshn.

00:09:15.064 --> 00:09:18.331
nu, OSO-, ven s'zaynen ofitsern gevezn.

00:09:19.080 --> 00:09:22.432
nit di proste soldatn flegn shteyn, nor di ofitsern.

00:09:23.248 --> 00:09:25.098
iz, in eyn ort

00:09:25.999 --> 00:09:29.183
hot, hobn zikh mentshn arumgeklibn

00:09:29.509 --> 00:09:31.038
arum a daytsh

00:09:31.551 --> 00:09:34.835
un zey hobn bay im genumen fregn frages.

00:09:38.048 --> 00:09:40.067
nor di hoypt frage iz gevezn,

00:09:40.444 --> 00:09:41.956
"vos vet ir ton

00:09:42.486 --> 00:09:43.830
mit di yidn?"

00:09:44.393 --> 00:09:46.631
vayle zey hobn dokh ale gevust az

00:09:47.211 --> 00:09:49.871
di ⟨TSE-⟩, di, di yidn...

00:09:50.417 --> 00:09:51.553
di daytshn

00:09:51.553 --> 00:09:54.227
hargenen avek di yidn, UNK,

00:09:54.227 --> 00:09:57.870
shikt zey in di C- CAMPn.

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:01.971
makht er,... un ikh shtey oykhet derbay...

00:10:02.044 --> 00:10:06.948
i- iz, er hot nit gevust az ikh bin a yid, un di poyerim hobn gevust, ober...

00:10:06.837 --> 00:10:09.159
ver hot gefregt? ⟨di⟩ poyerim?

00:10:08.085 --> 00:10:11.977
di poyerim, di poyerim. nit keyn yid vet fregn; a poyer hot gefregt.

00:10:13.367 --> 00:10:15.285
UNK zogt er, az

00:10:16.067 --> 00:10:19.673
gezunte, yunge ⟨y-⟩ veln arbetn.

00:10:20.067 --> 00:10:22.288
alte, shvakhe, kranke

00:10:22.665 --> 00:10:23.739
vet men u-

00:10:24.032 --> 00:10:25.241
umbrengen.

00:10:25.467 --> 00:10:27.131
azoy hot ir gehert?

